General.Name: African Gold Ltd
General.Description: African Gold Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in acquiring, exploring, evaluating, and exploiting mineral resource projects in Africa. The company explores for gold, nickel, cobalt, copper, caesium, lithium, tantalum, niobium, and beryllium deposits. Its flagship project is the Didievi gold project located in Côte d'Ivoire. African Gold Limited was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
